commentaries.commentary: A beautiful pass into the box! And...
GOAL! Bastian Schweinsteiger with a fantastic header! The crowd erupts as Bayern Munich takes the lead!
Let's take another look at that goal.
The Bayern Munich players are ecstatic!
Bayern on the attack! Robben weaves through the defense...
And Robben shoots! Oh, a fantastic save by De Gea! What a stop to deny Bayern!
Again, that incredible save from De Gea.
Fellaini rises high! A crucial header to clear the danger for United.
